Step 3
Upward Phase: Exhale and slowly flex (bend) your elbows by pulling your entire body towards your hands. Your elbows should remain in front of and pointed away from your body and your wrists should remain in the neutral position. Maintain a stiff torso aligning your head and spine, and avoid any sagging or aching in your low back or hips.
